---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import sonny from "../assets/images/sonny.webp"
import catering from "../assets/images/catering.webp"
import dessert from "../assets/images/dessert.webp"
---
<MainLayout>
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-10">
    <p class="text-lg text-black my-1 tracking-[0.02em] text-left mb-4 mt-10">
      <span class="text-3xl font-regular">ABOUT</span> 
    </p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-10">
      <p class="text-lg text-black my-1 leading-relaxed text-left">
        Balash was born from a spontaneous idea shared by three friends—Bertram, Emil, and Vincent—whose paths first crossed in the world of hospitality.
        Emil, a chef driven by culinary creativity, crafts the flavors behind each experience. Bertram, a connoisseur of wine and impeccable service, ensures that every detail is seamlessly executed. Vincent, with expertise in event planning, brings their shared vision to life.
        What began as a single pop-up at Pio Vin has since evolved into a full-fledged event company, dedicated to curating gastronomic experiences that feel both intimate and unforgettable.
      </p>
      <p class="text-lg text-black my-1 leading-relaxed text-left">
        What started as a single pop-up at Pio Vin has grown into a full-fledged event company, dedicated to crafting unforgettable gastronomic experiences.
        Rooted in the Arabic word for "giving without expectation," <span class="font-semibold">Balash</span> embodies our philosophy of generosity. While not free, our dining experiences feel like gifts—thoughtfully curated, rich in seasonal ingredients, and infused with warmth, quality, and a touch of Balash.
      </p>
    </div>
<!-- Sektioner med opdateret styling -->
<div class="space-y-12 text-center"> <!-- Øget plads mellem sektioner -->
  <!-- PRIVATE EVENTS -->
  <div>
    <h3 class="text-lg text-black my-1 text-left"> <!-- Venstrejusteret overskrift -->
      ( PRIVATE EVENTS )
    </h3>
    <hr class="border-t border-gray-300 mt-4 mb-6" /> <!-- Mere afstand omkring linjen -->

    <!-- Billede til højre og tekst til venstre -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 items-end">
      <!-- Tekst til venstre -->
      <div class="pb-2 text-black">
        <p class="text-left">
          Chef Emil Dos Santos and Balash offer a unique, personalized experience for your private events.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Billede til højre -->
      <div>
        <img src={catering.src} alt="catering" class="w-full h-auto object-cover" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="border-t border-gray-300 mt-4 mb-6" /> <!-- Mere afstand omkring linjen -->
  </div>

  <!-- POP UP DINING -->
  <div>
    <h3 class="text-lg text-black my-1 text-left"> <!-- Venstrejusteret overskrift -->
      ( POP UP DINING )
    </h3>
    <hr class="border-t border-gray-300 mt-4 mb-6" /> <!-- Mere afstand omkring linjen -->

    <!-- Billede til højre og tekst til venstre -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 items-end">
      <!-- Tekst til venstre -->
      <div class="pb-2 text-black">
        <p class="text-left">
          Our signature concept, where we bring “Balash” to new and exciting locations. With a personal and attentive approach, we make sure every guest feels welcome. We prioritize sustainability by minimizing food waste and working closely with local suppliers. Whether it’s an intimate gathering or a larger event.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Billede til højre -->
      <div>
        <img src={sonny.src} alt="sonny" class="w-full h-auto object-cover" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="border-t border-gray-300 mt-4 mb-6" /> <!-- Mere afstand omkring linjen -->
  </div>

  <!-- CATERING -->
  <div>
    <h3 class="text-lg text-black my-1 text-left"> <!-- Venstrejusteret overskrift -->
      ( CATERING )
    </h3>
    <hr class="border-t border-gray-300 mt-4 mb-6" /> <!-- Mere afstand omkring linjen -->

    <!-- Billede til højre og tekst til venstre -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 items-end">
      <!-- Tekst til venstre -->
      <div class="pb-2 text-black">
        <p class="text-left">
          We offer catering for your next celebration, reception, or dinner with friends and family. We provide customized menus, each one designed with seasonal ingredients and tailored to your specific wishes. Have a special occasion or a unique idea in mind?
        </p>
        <p class="text-left">
          If you have any questions, feel free to <a href="/contact" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">contact us</a>.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Billede til højre -->
      <div>
        <img src={dessert.src} alt="dessert" class="w-full h-auto object-cover" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="border-t border-gray-300 mt-4 mb-6" /> <!-- Mere afstand omkring linjen -->
  </div>
</div>

</MainLayout>

